rows.label: tlk45450111_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Me and Harghal, we both have
a flair for dancing.

rows.label: tlk45450111_03_msg0002
rows.name:
That's why Bahn-sama took such a shine
to us, and now we're his personal
dancing girls and secretaries.

rows.label: tlk45450111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Though if I'm honest, I think he likes
Harghal more than he likes me.

rows.label: tlk45450111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
At any rate, I'm grateful for how well
he treats us, and I enjoy the work.

rows.label: tlk45450111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I almost wish life could go on
like this forever.
